NK040(thi)052:1: // dam pa rgya gar dang ma cig lab sgron yum
NK040(thi)052:2: chen mo rnams kyi gtor dbang gi kha 'phang rnams
NK040(thi)052:3: bzhugs so // dam pa'i gtor dbang byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)052:5: gtor ma mi dmigs pa'i ngang las /
NK040(thi)052:6: pad zla'i steng du dam pa rgya gar sku mdog dmar smug seng ldeng gi mdog lta bu /
NK040(thi)052:7: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas pas d+aa ma ru /
NK040(thi)052:8: g.yon na mi rkang gling bu 'bud pa /
NK040(thi)052:10: de'i spyi bor brgyud pa'i bla ma /
NK040(thi)052:15: skabs na d+aak+ki rnams kyis bskor ba bsgom /
NK040(thi)052:16: de nas gsol 'debs kyi lan mo mdzod /
NK040(thi)052:17: rje bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)052:18: bka' brgyud pa rnams la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)052:19: dgos bka' drin can gyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)052:20: gnas ya ki ya ki ya ki nas //
NK040(thi)052:21: phyi bskor gcig bskor gnyis bskor dang gsum //
NK040(thi)052:22: phyi bskor ba lcags ri mu khyud bskor //
NK040(thi)052:23: bar bskor ba lho rgyal 'dzam bu'i gling //
NK040(thi)052:24: nang bskor ba deng ri bla 'khor nas //
NK040(thi)052:25: ri mkhan pa khrod kyi dgon pa ru //
NK040(thi)052:27: de na su bzhugs su ma bzhugs //
NK040(thi)052:28: de na dam pa rgya gar bzhugs //
NK040(thi)052:29: khong bzhugs pa chos nyid ngang der bzhugs //
NK040(thi)052:30: mdzad pa sems can 'gro don mdzad //
NK040(thi)052:31: sku 'khrungs pa rgya gar yul du bzhugs //
NK040(thi)052:32: gsung bsgrags pa bod yul dbus su bsgrags //
NK040(thi)052:33: chags pheb pa deng ri dgon du phebs //
NK040(thi)052:35: smra ba'i seng+ge mtshungs pa med //
NK040(thi)052:36: dpal chen b+hir+ya drod tshad mkhan //
NK040(thi)052:37: ar+ya de ba sgra tshad mkhan //
NK040(thi)052:38: dam pa mu stegs rgyud sde mkhan //
NK040(thi)052:39: rje mi pham mgon po bcom ldan 'das //
NK040(thi)052:40: khong 'dzam bu gling gis rgyan gcig po //
NK040(thi)052:41: rje der bzhugs dam pa la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)052:42: der bzhugs dam pas byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)052:43: khong steng der bka' brgyud thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)052:44: bar der lha tshogs khrigs se khrig /
NK040(thi)052:45: g.yas der dpa' bo ngar dang bcas //
NK040(thi)052:46: g.yon der dpa' mo ngar dang ldan //
NK040(thi)052:47: mdun der dam can dpungs se dpung //
NK040(thi)052:48: skabs der d+aak+ki shigs se shig /
NK040(thi)052:49: 'og der gdon tshogs mya la la //
NK040(thi)052:50: rje der bzhugs dam pa la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)052:51: rje der bzhugs dam pas byin rlabs kyi chu bo rgyun mi chad //
NK040(thi)052:52: rje drung na bzhugs na gus phyag 'tshal //
NK040(thi)052:53: rgyab na bzhugs na mos phyag 'tshal //
NK040(thi)052:54: mos gus kyi phyag la nye ring med //
NK040(thi)052:55: gsol ba snying gi dkyil nas 'debs //
NK040(thi)052:56: byin rlabs thugs kyi klong nas stsol //
NK040(thi)052:57: sku'i byin rlabs lus la zhugs //
NK040(thi)052:58: lus la bde drod 'bar du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:59: lus kyi sgrib pa sbyang du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:60: sprul sku thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:61: gsung gis byin rlabs ngag la zhugs //
NK040(thi)052:63: ngag gis sgrib pa dag nas kyang //
NK040(thi)052:64: longs sku thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:65: thugs kyi byin rlabs sems la zhugs //
NK040(thi)052:66: sems la rtog pa 'char du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:67: yid kyi sgrib pa dag nas kyang //
NK040(thi)052:68: chos sku thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:69: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum //
NK040(thi)052:70: dug gsum ngang gis zhig tu gsol //
NK040(thi)052:71: rkyen pho gdon mo gdon klu gdon gsum //
NK040(thi)052:72: gdon gsum rnam rtog yal du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:73: nad rlung mkhris 'dus pa bad kan bzhi //
NK040(thi)052:74: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams bsal du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:75: chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum //
NK040(thi)052:76: sku gsum mngon du 'byung du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:77: gzhan don dpag med 'byung du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:78: rje der bzhugs rje der bzhugs dam pas pha nag po chen po gzi mdangs can //
NK040(thi)052:80: de bdud bzhi zil gyis non pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:82: de 'khrul bzhi rtsad nas bcad pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:83: zhabs gnyis rba bran gshib pa 'dra //
NK040(thi)052:84: de byang chub lam la zhugs pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:85: sku mdog nag po smug pa ni //
NK040(thi)052:86: de chos nyid ngang la bzhugs pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:87: dbu skra khams nag gyen du 'khyil //
NK040(thi)052:88: de mtho ris thar lam phyed pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:89: spyan rtsa dmar la 'khrug pa ni //
NK040(thi)052:90: de stong gsum kun la gzigs pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:91: shangs rgyud ring la shang rtse rno ba de //
NK040(thi)052:92: de theg chen gyis rgyud don rtogs pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:93: tshems mdog dkar la tshem rtse rno //
NK040(thi)052:94: de skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:95: phyag sor ring la phyag sen rno //
NK040(thi)052:96: de ser sna mdud pa grol ba'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:97: zhabs sor seng phrug bkram pa 'dra //
NK040(thi)052:98: skal ldan thugs rjes 'dzin pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:99: rje der bzhugs dam pa la rje der bzhugs dam pas rje re res nyin mtshan 'khor bar gzim //
NK040(thi)052:100: nyin mtshan 'khor bar gzim tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:101: chos gnyug ma rgyun chad med pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:102: rje re res rten 'brel sna tshogs mdzad //
NK040(thi)052:103: rten 'brel sna tshogs mdzad tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:104: bka' 'khor gyi bar chad bsal ba'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:105: rje re res smyon pa'i brtul zhugs mdzad //
NK040(thi)052:106: smyon pa'i brtul zhugs mdzad tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:107: rkyen pho gdon mo gdon 'dul ba'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:108: rje re res rgya gram srang du gzim //
NK040(thi)052:109: rgya gram srang du gzim tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:110: de theg dman gyi zil gyis gnon pa'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:111: rje re res ras gos rkyang cig mnab //
NK040(thi)052:112: ras gos rkyang cig mnab tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:113: bde drod lus la sbar ba'i brda //
NK040(thi)052:114: rje der bzhugs dam pa la rje der bzhugs dam pas bdag lus ngag yid gsum mchod par bul //
NK040(thi)052:115: lus la bde drod 'bar du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:116: ngag la nus pa 'bar du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:117: sems la rtogs pa 'char du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:118: rje drung na bzhugs na drung phyag 'tshal //
NK040(thi)052:119: rgyang la bzhugs na mos phyag 'tshal //
NK040(thi)052:120: mos gus kyi phyag la nye ring med //
NK040(thi)052:121: mkha' spyod gnas su lam sna drongs //
NK040(thi)052:122: u rgyan gnas su lam sna drongs //
NK040(thi)052:123: rkyen phyi yi bar chad phyi nas sel //
NK040(thi)052:124: nang gis bar chad nang la sel //
NK040(thi)052:125: rkyen ngan pa byang chub grogs su bsgyur //
NK040(thi)052:126: 'gal rkyen mthun rkyen dam pa bsgyur du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:128: pha dam pa'i rtags bstod jo mos mdzad pa rdzogs so ////
NK040(thi)052:129: de nas ma cig lab sgron gyis dbang khrid byed pa la /
NK040(thi)052:130: dang po gtor ma spyi bor bzhag cing chu blug la /
NK040(thi)052:131: da khyed rang rnams kyi 'di ltar bsgom la /
NK040(thi)052:132: gtor ma mi dmigs pa las /
NK040(thi)052:133: pad+ma zla ba nyi ma'i gdan la /
NK040(thi)052:134: rtsa ba'i bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i ma
NK040(thi)052:135: cig lab kyi sgron ma sku mdog dkar mo gangs
NK040(thi)052:136: ri la nyi ma shar ba ltar dkar la /
NK040(thi)052:138: g.yas gser gyi d+aa ma ru /
NK040(thi)052:139: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK040(thi)052:140: sku la ras phrug dkar po'i na bza' mnab pa dbu skra sil mas sku rgyab non pa /
NK040(thi)052:141: zhabs sems dpa'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)052:142: mtshan dang dpe byad 'od zer dang ldan par bsgom /
NK040(thi)052:143: de'i phyi rol na shar na rdo rje mkha' 'gro la /
NK040(thi)052:144: rdo rje mkha' 'gro 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK040(thi)052:146: rin chen mkha' 'gro 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK040(thi)052:149: byang du las kyi mkha' 'gro la /
NK040(thi)052:150: las kyi mkha' 'gro 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK040(thi)052:151: de'i phyi rol du sha za'i mkha' 'gro dang 'jig
NK040(thi)052:152: rten mkha' 'gro sprin dpung gtib pa ltar bsgom pa'i
NK040(thi)052:153: mos pa mdzod / gsol 'debs kyi lad mo mdzod /
NK040(thi)052:154: ma yum chen thugs las sprul pa'i sras //
NK040(thi)052:155: ma cig ja mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK040(thi)052:156: pha rol phyin pa'i grub thob ma //
NK040(thi)052:157: skal ldan kun gyi rgyud grol ma //
NK040(thi)052:158: byin gyis rlabs par mdzad du gsol //
NK040(thi)052:159: sku lus chung la gzi mdangs can //
NK040(thi)052:160: sku mdog dkar la 'od zer can //
NK040(thi)052:161: skye ba dman la dgongs pa mtho //
NK040(thi)052:162: kun dang mthun pa'i spyod pa can //
NK040(thi)052:163: byin gyis brlab par dus gsum sangs rgyas gdung 'dzin ma //
NK040(thi)052:164: bdag dang mos pa'i bu slob rnams //
NK040(thi)052:165: byin gyis ser sna med pa'i don rtogs shing //
NK040(thi)052:166: pha rol phyin pa'i blo mtho ma //
NK040(thi)052:167: bdag dang mos pa'i bu slob rnams //
NK040(thi)052:168: byin gyis ma rang byung ye shes don rtogs shing //
NK040(thi)052:169: nyams pa med pa'i khrims srung ma //
NK040(thi)052:170: bdag dang byin gyis ma chags zhen med pa'i don rtogs shing //
NK040(thi)052:171: skye med bzod pa bsgom mdzad ma //
NK040(thi)052:172: bdag dang byin gyis ma gnas brtsal med pa'i don rtogs shing //
NK040(thi)052:174: bdag dang byin gyis ma yengs ba med pa'i don rtogs shing //
NK040(thi)052:175: yengs med bsam gtan sgom mdzad ma //
NK040(thi)052:176: bdag dang byin gyis ma kun gyi rang bzhin don rtogs shing //
NK040(thi)052:177: bdag med shes pa'i rnal 'byor ma //
NK040(thi)052:178: bdag dang byin gyis ma phyogs med lta ba zhan pa grol //
NK040(thi)052:179: mnyam nyid rtogs pas dmigs pa grol //
NK040(thi)052:180: ma rtog med rtogs pas nyams nga grol //
NK040(thi)052:181: bdag dang byin gyis rlabs ma stong nyid ngang la gzigs tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:182: nyon mongs spang nas ye sangs rgyas //
NK040(thi)052:184: bdag dang byin gyis ma mnyam nyid ngang du bzhugs tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:185: rje bo rtog pa'i nyams dang ldan //
NK040(thi)052:187: nyams dbyangs mgur ma 'u ru ru //
NK040(thi)052:188: byin rlab na bun thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)052:189: ma dgongs pa shar du spyod tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:190: don 'gyur ba med pa'i nyams dang ldan //
NK040(thi)052:192: mkha' 'gro dkar mo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)052:193: gsung dbyangs mgur ma 'u ru ru //
NK040(thi)052:194: gar dang rol mo khrigs se khrig /
NK040(thi)052:195: byin rlabs na bun gdam ngag sbrang char si li li //
NK040(thi)052:196: 'gro don phyogs med ya la la //
NK040(thi)052:197: bdag dang byin gyis ma dgongs pa lho ru spyod tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:198: yon tan rdzogs pa'i nyams dang ldan //
NK040(thi)052:200: mkha' 'gro ser mo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)052:201: gsung dbyangs gar dang rol mo byin rlabs na gdam
NK040(thi)052:202: ngag sbrang char 'gro don phyogs bdag dang byin gyis
NK040(thi)052:203: ma dgongs pa nub tu spyod tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:204: don chags pa med pa'i nyams dang ldan //
NK040(thi)052:205: pad+ma mkha' mkha' 'gro dmar mo'i gsung dbyangs gar dang
NK040(thi)052:206: rol mo byin rlabs na bun gdam ngag sbrang char
NK040(thi)052:207: 'gro don phyogs med ya la bdag dang byin gyis
NK040(thi)052:208: rlabs ma dgongs pa byang du spyod tsam na //
NK040(thi)052:209: don 'gyur ba med pa'i las kyi mkha' 'gro 'bum
NK040(thi)052:210: mkha' 'gro ljang ku'i tshogs gsung dbyangs gar dang byin
NK040(thi)052:211: rlabs gdam ngag 'gro don bdag dang byin gyis ma
NK040(thi)052:212: dgongs pa dbus su byon tsa na //
NK040(thi)052:213: don mtha' dbus med pa'i nyams dang ldan //
NK040(thi)052:214: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro 'bum dang sku mdog mthing kha'i
NK040(thi)052:215: gsung gar dang byin gyis gdam ngag 'gro don bdag
NK040(thi)052:216: dang byin gyis ma yum chen thugs las sprul pa'i
NK040(thi)052:217: sras // ma cig jo mo rnal 'byor pha rol phyin pa'i grub thob ma //
NK040(thi)052:218: skal ldan kun gyi rgyud grol ma //
NK040(thi)052:219: skal med thar pa'i lam 'dren ma //
NK040(thi)052:221: mtho spyi gtsug rgyan der bzhugs su gsol //
NK040(thi)052:222: bzhugs nas byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK040(thi)052:223: ma chos dbyings nam mkha' yangs pa'i pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)052:224: thugs rje sprin thung thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)052:225: shes rab kyi 'od ta le ba //
NK040(thi)052:226: nyams myong na bun thibs se thib //
NK040(thi)052:227: byin rlab char rgyun si li li //
NK040(thi)052:228: byin gyis rlobs shig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)052:229: bar chad sol cig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)052:230: dbang mchog bskur cig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)052:231: dngos grub stsol cig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)052:232: lam sna drongs shig ma cig ma //
NK040(thi)052:233: kyee ma mi min ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)052:234: lab kyi sgron ma de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)052:235: 'og min gnas su lam sna drongs //
NK040(thi)052:236: o rgyan gnas su lam sna drongs //
NK040(thi)052:237: mkha' spyod gnas su stong nyid dbyings su ma mi min ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)052:238: shar nas gom gsum byon pa'i tshe //
NK040(thi)052:239: sku lus chung la sku mdog dkar //
NK040(thi)052:240: rdo rje mkha' 'gro dzahmh'u bam hos gnas 'dir byon /
NK040(thi)052:242: ma mi min ye shes mkha' 'gro ma /
NK040(thi)052:244: lab kyi sgron ma khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)052:245: 'og min gnas su lam sna drongs //
NK040(thi)052:246: u rgyan gnas su lho'i nub nas byang dbus su sogs 'gres so //
NK040(thi)052:247: de nas ma cig 'od du zhu nas gtor chu blug /
NK040(thi)052:249: yum chen pha rol phyin ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)052:250: yum chen gyi gtor dbang bla ma'i phyag len ltar /
NK040(thi)052:251: nyams su len bde bri bar bya /
NK040(thi)052:252: 'di la sbyor ba dngos gzhi rjes gsum mo //
NK040(thi)052:253: thog mar sbyor ba'i cho ga ni /
NK040(thi)052:254: sngon du gtor ma zla gam bang rim gsum pa byas la /
NK040(thi)052:255: cog zlum nyi zla ril bu nor bus brgyan pa'i dbus su bshams /
NK040(thi)052:256: phyogs bzhi bshos bran bzhi bzhag la /
NK040(thi)052:257: sha thud kyis legs par brgyan cing bshams /
NK040(thi)052:258: gzhan yang rnam lnga dang cha bzhir gtor ma dang /
NK040(thi)052:259: mchod pa grangs mang pos mtha' bskor /
NK040(thi)052:261: de nas gsang 'dus gtor bsngo mchod pa yan chad tshang bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)052:262: de nas yan lag brgyad pa dang thun mong gi skyabs 'gro sems bskyed rgyas par bya'o //
NK040(thi)052:263: de nas gtor ma slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag la dmigs pa 'di ltar mdzod /
NK040(thi)052:265: khyed rang rnams kyi mgo thog gi gtor gzhong de
NK040(thi)052:266: nyid mi dmigs pa las thar pa chen po'i gzhal
NK040(thi)052:267: yas khang gi dbus su nyi zla'i gdan la ma
NK040(thi)052:268: cig lab sgron sku mdog gangs ril nyi ma shar
NK040(thi)052:269: ba lta bu zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK040(thi)052:270: g.yas gser gyi d+aa ma ru /
NK040(thi)052:271: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu /
NK040(thi)052:272: zhabs sems dpa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)052:273: de'i spyi bor yum chen mo gser gyi mdog 'dra ba /
NK040(thi)052:275: g.yas dang po gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK040(thi)052:276: 'og mas shes rab kyi ral gri /
NK040(thi)052:278: 'og mas shes rab kyi po ti bsnam pa /
NK040(thi)052:279: zhabs rdo rje'i dkyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)052:280: ma cig gis g.yas phyogs su bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya
NK040(thi)052:281: thub pa sku mdog gser btso ma'i mdog lta bu
NK040(thi)052:283: g.yas sa non g.yon mnyam bzhag mdzad pa /
NK040(thi)052:284: zhabs rdo rje'i dkyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)052:285: g.yon du 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng+ge sku mdog ser po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK040(thi)052:286: g.yas pas shes rab kyi ral gri /
NK040(thi)052:287: g.yon du me tog pad+ma dkar po'i khar po ti bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)052:288: zhabs rdo rje'i dkyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)052:289: yum sras de bzhi la mdun nas g.yas bskor du pad zla'i gdan la /
NK040(thi)052:292: skyo ston bsod nams bla ma /
NK040(thi)052:293: ma cig lab kyi sgron ma /
NK040(thi)052:295: pha cig dam pa zang thal /
NK040(thi)052:296: rje btsun rgya nag gcer bu /
NK040(thi)052:298: sangs rgyas dge slong sangs rgyas ras pa /
NK040(thi)052:302: slob dpon shes rab bla ma /
NK040(thi)052:304: rtog ldan nam mkha' rdo rje /
NK040(thi)052:305: skyes mchog tshul khrims rgyal mtshan /
NK040(thi)052:306: mtshungs med chos kyi rdo rje /
NK040(thi)052:307: drin chen rtsa ba'i bla ma /
NK040(thi)052:308: dz+ny+aa na ke tu la sogs grub thob gcod kyi brgyud pa rnams kyi bskor ba /
NK040(thi)052:309: gzhan yang sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dpag tu med pas bskor ba bsgom la /
NK040(thi)052:310: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku la 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum dang /
NK040(thi)052:311: gzhan yang sku'i cha nas khro chung phyag mtshan rdo rje'i tshogs dpag tu med pa byung nas /
NK040(thi)052:312: khyed rang rnams kyi lus ngag yid gsum la thim par bsam la mos pa brtse gcig tu gyis /
NK040(thi)052:313: gsol ba 'debs pa'i lad mo gyis /
NK040(thi)052:314: yum chen shes rab phar phyin la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)052:315: skye med chos kyi sku la gsol ba 'debs //
NK040(thi)052:316: rgyal ba sh+aakya'i rgyal po la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)052:317: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams la 'jam dpal smra ba'i
NK040(thi)052:318: seng+ge la rgyal sras 'phags pa rnams la rje btsun
NK040(thi)052:319: ar+ya de ba la 'dzam gling skyes mchog rnams la
NK040(thi)052:320: gsol pa gcig dam pa rgya gar la rgya gar
NK040(thi)052:321: grub chen rnams la skyo ston bsod nams bla ma
NK040(thi)052:322: bod yul skyes mchog rnams la ma cig lab kyi
NK040(thi)052:323: sgron ma la ye shes mkha' 'gro rnams la khu
NK040(thi)052:324: bsgom chos kyi seng+ge la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)052:325: skye med don ston rnams la pha gcig dol pa
NK040(thi)052:326: zang thal la skyes chen don 'grub rnams la rje
NK040(thi)052:327: btsun rgya nag gcer bu la rnal 'byor 'khrul zhig
NK040(thi)052:328: rnams la mkhas pa sangs rgyas rab ston la mkhas
NK040(thi)052:329: grub chen po rnams la sangs rgyas dge slong la
NK040(thi)052:330: tshul khrims mthar phyin rnams sangs rgyas sum pa ras
NK040(thi)052:331: chen la brtul zhugs grub pa rnams la sangs rgyas
NK040(thi)052:332: gnyen ston la chos kyi spyan ldan rnams la ras
NK040(thi)052:333: pa chos kyi seng+ge la rnal 'byor dbang phyug rnams
NK040(thi)052:334: la rje btsun badz+ra seng+ha la dam chos smra ba
NK040(thi)052:335: rnams la slob dpon pra dz+ny+aa gu ru la rtog
NK040(thi)052:336: ldan dam pa rnams la chos rje badz+ra sh+ri la
NK040(thi)052:337: sogs pa'i // 'gro ba'i mgon po rnams la //
NK040(thi)052:338: rtogs ldan nam mkha' rdo rje la don gnyis grub
NK040(thi)052:339: pa rnams la skyes mchog tshul khrims rgyal mtshan la
NK040(thi)052:340: bskyed rdzogs bstan thob rnams la mtshungs med chos kyi
NK040(thi)052:341: rdo rje la sdom gsum mthar phyin rnams la rin
NK040(thi)052:342: chen dz+ny+aa na ke tu la mkhas btsun dam pa
NK040(thi)052:343: rnams la drin chen rtsa ba'i bla ma la grub
NK040(thi)052:344: thob brgyud pa rnams la thar pa'i lam ston rnams
NK040(thi)052:345: la phan bde'i 'byung gnas rnams la 'phags pa'i dge
NK040(thi)052:346: 'dun rnams la bdag sogs mkha' khyab 'gro ba rnams
NK040(thi)052:347: // sems can ma rig 'khrul pa sang bar byin gyis rlobs //
NK040(thi)052:348: gzung 'dzin mdud pa grol bar byin gyis rlobs ////
NK040(thi)052:350: de nas ma cig 'od du zhu nas gtor chu blud /
